      "markdown": "_look指，从外表上看，eem指内心的判断：appeor.指给人以表面的印象.\n\nappear wise, look Uke his father.\n\na \n\n\n\n107. gather ,collect \n\ngather把分散的东西集中到一起，colect指精心地、有选择地进行收集\n\ncollect stamps.\n\n\n\n108. mean to do, mean doing mean to do 打算，想要做某事；mean doing意思是，意味着.By this I mean giving the students more practice.\n\n109. die from, die of die from表示死手(枪)伤，虚弱，过度劳累饮食过度等.die of表示死于'E 110.pay for,pay bko 司ab pay for 为…付钱；payback还钱，但不一定还清；pay off还请.\n\n11. divide, separate \n\ndivide把一个整体分成几部分，separate把连在一起的个体分开.\n\ndivide the apple, separarte the houses.\n\n\n\n112.arrive, get, reach \n\narrive 不及物动词，后接in(大地点)，at(小地点)；get 不及物动词后\n\n]\n\n\n\ngrow使某种植物在某地生长着或使其发展下去；plant移植，移栽已经长成苗的植物Plant the tree，tress are growing.\n\n114.manage, try manage to do设法做成了某事;ry to do尽力去做某事，但不一定成功.He tried to pass the examled ",
